name: ircclient
description: ircclient made with electron and react

releases.name: Alpha v2.1.0
releases.body:
### Fixes / Changes
- Redo the model using ES6 classes
- Easier to manage data
- Parting and multi servers now do not get jumbled up in the data

`## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","nick":"client_v1","channels":["#client_test"]}`

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.5
releases.body:
### Fixes
- Fix quit for multi servers

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.4
releases.body:
### Fixes
- Fix the quit/part when a user leaves the server/channel
- Nick changes fixed

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.3
releases.body:
### Fixes
- The ping send command was written wrong.

#### Note

New way to connect to server. userName changed to nick
`## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","nick":"client_v1","channels":["#blubot_test"]}`

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.2
releases.body:
### Fixes
- Fix userlist to remove empty user
- Fix userlist to be sorted alphabetacally
- Add /part and /quit commands

#### Note

New way to connect to server. userName changed to nick
`## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","nick":"client_v1","channels":["#blubot_test"]}`

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.1
releases.body:
### Fixes
- What was broken before is now fixed.
- All commands back in working order

releases.name: Alpha v2.0.0
releases.body:
### Fixes/Changes
- Wrote own irc module for parsing and connecting to irc
- Added OSX zip
- Cleaner way to send back to the irc server
- All pure RAW commands.

**Note**
New way to connect to server. userName changed to nick
 `## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","nick":"client_v1","channels":["#blubot_test"]}`

### Bugs
- /msg is broken
- PMs have not been tested but highly likely it is broken

releases.name: Alpha v1.2.1
releases.body:
### Fixes
- last version had annoying user join = new room bug

releases.name: Alpha v1.2.0
releases.body:
### Fixes
- multi server support.

Fully functional multi server support so far. Connect like the last builds but can do it twice.

Example commands to connect to server:

`## {"server":"irc.ringoflightning.net","userName":"client_v1","channels":["#client"]}`
`## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","userName":"client_v1","channels":["#blubot_test"]}`

releases.name: Alpha v1.1.6
releases.body:
### Fixes
- Hopefully last fix for duplicate rooms
- Fixed issues with pms that came due to a fix with the duplicate rooms

releases.name: Alpha v1.1.3
releases.body:
### Fixes
- fix deps

File is now smaller

releases.name: Alpha v1.1.2
releases.body:
### Fixes
- Rewrite how replies are handled
- fix ACTION commands
- PM bug fix
- Most bugs are fixed

releases.name: Alpha v1.1.1
releases.body:
#### Fixes:
- Added colors
- tab completion for nicks
- fixed pm's (I think)
- proper nick highlighting in messages
- fixed QUIT and JOIN. PART still missing
- ability to change nicks

example initial: `## {"server":"irc.freenode.net","userName":"client_v1","channels":["#blubot_test"]}`
